abstract: International House Hunting column; recently renovated 150-year-old farmhouse with four bedrooms in County Cork, Ireland, is listed at $678,000; information about market and tips for buying properties in West Cork, Ireland highlighted.
snippet: The West Cork housing market began to rebound last year after an extended downturn that stretched from 2007 to 2014.
lead_paragraph: The West Cork housing market began to rebound last year after an extended downturn that stretched from 2007 to 2014.
